highlights.text: “ME! (feat. Brendon Urie of Panic! At The Disco)” by Taylor Swift, Brendon Urie, and Panic! At The Disco is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 121 weeks straight.
Billie Eilish has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “bad guy” is the highest at #1.
